.TH IBHCACOUNTERS 8 "September 10, 2010" "Pragmatic Infiniband Utilities" "Infiniband Diagnostics"

.SH NAME
ibhcacounters \- Read sysfs counters from IB HCA's

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ibhcacounters [-hca]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
ibhcacounters queries sysfs for various IB HCA's for internal debug counters.

For details on the meanings of these counters see your HCA vendor.

.SH OPTIONS

.PP
.TP
\fB\-h\fR
print help message
.TP
\fB\-c\fR
clear counters after querying them
.TP
\fB\-a\fR
Report "all" counters event if they are "0".  The default is to only print
counters which are non-zero.

.SH REQUIREMENTS
.PP
.TP
\fBsysfs\fR

